reviewText: This is one of my favorite Joan Fontaine movies. It's a mystery to me why this is one of her lesser known movies. This is a region 2 DVD and plays just fine on a region free DVD player. At least, on my LG region free DVD player. The picture and sound of this particular transfer are both top notch. A rarely seen Joan Fontaine movie for $10.00 is a good find. And, I, for one, am glad to have found it.
